  "pageTitle": "配备数字驾驶舱的资源回收中心",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-ai\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">智能回收箱 详情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">配备数字驾驶舱的资源回收中心</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">参考资料：一个资源回收中心，结合了分拣模块、称重、报告和远程操作可视化。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"smart-recovery-center\" aria-labelledby=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">参考时间线</p>\n          <h2 id=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\">从混合接收到数字化运营可视化</h2>\n          <p>案例按买方评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解以及对比前后对比。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 详情 时间线\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p>\n              <h3>混合回收物流需要数据支持路由</h3>\n              <p>该中心结合了接收、物料分拣、分类、称重、存储和出境物流，涵盖混合可回收和市政废弃物流。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>工作流程区域</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 区域</strong><span>接收到外发</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>物料范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 流</strong><span>可回收物与市政废弃物</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p>\n              <h3>匿名市级回收服务提供商</h3>\n              <p>合作单位需要对进料物料、分选产出、每日运行状态及管理审查报告的更好可视性。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>管理层</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 驾驶舱</strong><span>中央操作显示</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>评测模式</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">每日</strong><span>输出与状态报告</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p>\n              <h3>物理流和数据流必须保持同步</h3>\n              <p>该项目必须连接分拣模块、称重点、驾驶舱显示、存储区和远程管理，同时不将操作与报告分离。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>数据点</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 群</strong><span>输入 / 输出 / 状态</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>远程需求</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 接口</strong><span>管理可见度</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p>\n              <h3>分拣模块加上称重和数字驾驶舱</h3>\n              <p>参考包涵盖分拣模块、智能称重点、驾驶舱显示、远程管理界面，以及报告 支持的吞吐量和类别。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>系统区块</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 块</strong><span>分类/称重/报告/管理</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>输出视图</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 仪表盘</strong><span>驾驶舱简介</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p>\n              <h3>操作可见性成为案件证据的一部分</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>分离的物料流与报告</strong><p>管理者对接收、分类和存储日常连接的了解有限。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之后</span><strong>从接收到报告的可见路径</strong><p>参考视频和驾驶舱截图展示了物料路线、分选产出和报告工作流程。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>证据集</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 资产</strong><span>视频和驾驶舱截图</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section ai-rfq-section\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
